<br>
Then, assuming good faction, one, two, or three people turn in the three staves. The last one to turn one in is handed a sealed bag. (Not a container, by the way, but have a slot open just in case.)<br>
<br>
Take that bag to Solomon, who is up on the third floor in the Temple of Sol Ro. Again, assuming sufficient faction, if you just hand it to him he'll give you your epic staff.<br>
<br>
If your faction is insufficient you can have a friend invis you after you open the trade window with the NPC's but before you hit &quot;give&quot;. Invis provides sufficient faction to complete the quest. <p><SELECT>
